  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Crazy Reindeer Hotel is offered on a half board basis.</p>
<p>A hot and cold buffet breakfast is available each morning (Weekdays 7.30 - 10am and weekends 7.30 - 10.30am).</p>
<p>Each evening you can enjoy a buffet style three course dinner, which is taken in the 'Taivas' Sky Restaurant. There is a wide choice of food available and this is usually open between 5pm - 8pm.</p>
<p>The hotel has four à la carte restaurants where guests receive a 20% discount on a 3 course meal, if they wish to dine in them. Guests should inform reception the night before they will not be eating the normal half board dinner. These restaurants are:</p>
<ul>
<li>'Sapuska' Fondue &amp; Grill restaurant serving Alp specialties </li>
<li>'Pihripirtti' Steakhouse </li>
<li>Ristorante Renna Pizza &amp; Pasta restaurant </li>
<li>Wanha Hullu Poro Rock Café burger &amp; grill restaurant</li>
</ul>
<p><span>Festive Feast included for all guests during December, for a Christmas celebration with games and music.</span></p>
<p> </p>]]></cateringDescription>
